panels.name: Kinesis API Calls Events by Region
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=pipeline/aws/cloudtrail "kinesis.amazonaws.com"
| json field=_raw "eventSource", "eventName", "awsRegion", "sourceIPAddress","userAgent" nodrop
| json field=_raw "requestParameters.streamName" as streamName nodrop
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.sessionContext.sessionIssuer.userName" as userName nodrop
| where eventSource="kinesis.amazonaws.com"
| count as count by awsRegion, eventName
| transpose row awsRegion column eventName

panels.name: Avg Iterator Age ms by Stream

metricsQueries.query: Namespace=AWS/Kinesis metric=GetRecords.IteratorAgeMilliseconds Statistic=Average 	| avg by StreamName
Namespace=AWS/Kinesis metric=GetRecords.Latency Statistic=Average 	| avg by StreamName

panels.name: Kinesis API Calls Summary Table
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=pipeline/aws/cloudtrail "kinesis.amazonaws.com"
| json field=_raw "eventSource", "eventName", "awsRegion", "sourceIPAddress","userAgent" nodrop
| json field=_raw "requestParameters.streamName" as streamName nodrop
| json field=_raw "userIdentity.sessionContext.sessionIssuer.userName" as userName nodrop
| where eventSource="kinesis.amazonaws.com"
| count as count by awsRegion, userName, eventName, sourceIPAddress
| sort by count
